{"tid":1238422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講左幾多次冇source唔好share，要做fact check。","createTime":"2019-06-17T22:24:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T06:23:02.000Z","uid":52817,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0b8e931e0db41a410740725b146f1ed0b2d8920b","tid":1238422,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T22:24:50.000Z","msg":"講左咁耐結果都仲係鳩既，我真係好失望，但趁而家謠言仲未散得出我希望快快手屌醒你地先。<br />\n<br />\n果個話義士死左既post，由頭到尾得樓主一個人講。俾人屌晒老母之後先話原來只係&quot;聽到護士講&quot;。呢個樓主一個post都冇開過，google剩係搵到係d水晶post <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/983203/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/983203/page/1</a> 留左句&quot;水晶棒你又唔信？&quot;。更何況佢只不過係聽到護士講，好明顯就唔係一個可靠既source來源。<br />\n<br />\n到後來又多左一個facebook post話&quot;收到風 佢過左身&quot;，又係所謂收到風，同我阿媽個仔係佢老婆個同事根本就冇分別，基本上就係9up。然後呢句又唔知點解俾人cap左去台灣ptt，變成有人死左但封鎖緊消息，到最尾ptt既9up又番番黎連登。<br />\n<br />\n我屌晒你地老母。 facebook果個人有183個朋友，其中大部份都係台灣人，然後6/14呢個fb人post左句(節錄) &quot;我就是不撤文，他本人一天沒能面對記者，我一天也不會放過。可悲的是有人還以為香港不可能發生被消失、馬上火化、不給予死亡證明文件的這種誇張事情。&quot; 咁imply左d乜野？即係ptt篇文極有可能就係呢個facebook人貼既，即係話義士死左既來源由頭到尾就係 呢兩個人，然後<span style=\"color: red;\">一個係收到風，一個係聽人講</span>。我不妨再陰謀論d，明屈你地，根本極有可能fb人同連登樓主係同一個人。<br />\n<br />\n講到尾，點解會有咁多人推post又盛，主因就係一d消息都冇，好多人關心義士，所以都想知真定假，謠言就係用左你地關心義士既心理先散播到。唔該你地自己諗下，如果真係過左身，係咪真係有可能封鎖到消息？係資訊發達既社會，要封鎖義士過身消息係咪真係咁容易？呢到係香港唔係中國，not yet呀。我明白各位對香港係好冇信心，但係都唔該理性分析下，單單係陳沛然事件就已經表明左，如果真有義士死左，醫院冇可能封鎖到消息。連建制派有個女議員屌林鄭老味都爆到出黎，你覺得醫院死左人真係鎖到消息？真心相信咁樣都可以靠收買鎖到消息既人，同相信遊行係收左錢行根本就冇分別。<br />\n<br />\n咁點解到而家連生/死消息都冇，點解冇記者問到？各位又不妨諗下而家有咩人先係最想搵到義士，係差人呀。eu醫生護士係發生左醫院拉人事件後，最應該做既就係保護所有傷者，身份status全部資料都應該保密，是但一個護士講左句佢身體安好，咪有線有料搵到佢係邊間醫院，正確既做法就係乜撚都唔知。<br />\n<br />\n呢個post一張圖都唔會有，因為唔想幫佢地share d 9up。<br />\n<br />\n唔該各位有心人唔好再推果埋謠言post，同埋收番埋你地既好奇心。你地既關心義士肯定會收到，但唔該唔好再俾壓力佢家人或身邊既人，同埋做好保護措施，唔好忘記而家仲有義士係面臨暴動罪既風險，你地一句想知可能隨時搞到人唔小心篤左灰。"},{"pid":"be8dc2ca1e87b688a4a9475635bacce366b0a71b","tid":1238422,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T22:48:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e95a2dc14edfef3c18e335d27211299cd692213b","tid":1238422,"uid":52817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T22:51:37.000Z","msg":"tl;dr:<br />\n1. 冇source唔好share<br />\n2. 如果有義士過身一定會爆到出黎鎖唔到消息<br />\n3. 保護義士唔好再叫佢報平安"},{"pid":"80e66a7171cf3634f4fec5aa693958aba4d1110a","tid":1238422,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T22:59:37.000Z","msg":"連登講到咁多人讀過大學都咁容易道聽塗說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇真憑實據嘅內容，甚至係有人9up、抹黑都可以信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />究竟你地班連登仔係咪讀緊屎片？當討論緊時局一定要有source先可以傾落去連咁都可以唔知？"},{"pid":"bb06ef6a04e105fd666137a6932e43fe79a96b84","tid":1238422,"uid":52817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"80e66a7171cf3634f4fec5aa693958aba4d1110a","tid":1238422,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T22:59:37.000Z","msg":"連登講到咁多人讀過大學都咁容易道聽塗說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇真憑實據嘅內容，甚至係有人9up、抹黑都可以信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />究竟你地班連登仔係咪讀緊屎片？當討論緊時局一定要有source先可以傾落去連咁都可以唔知？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T23:11:58.000Z","msg":"有好多人都明白既。不過都真係好多人想知到底義士點樣，結果無意中就幫左謠言傳播。<br />\n<br />\n呢個謠言最仆街既地方就係<br />\n1: 用左大部人對義士既關愛心，引導人就算冇source都會幫手share：<del>「有人話xx死左，係咪真架，有冇人幫手confirm」</del>結果就係間接散播緊謠言。<br />\n2: 因應香港愈來愈強國化，用陰謀論cover謠言本身靠唔住既地方：<del>「有人死左都冇人報？等係啦成個醫院都俾人收買晒，你以為香港唔會發生呢d事？香港已經唔係以前既香港喇。」</del><br />\n<br />\n用左刪除線廢事散謠言。"},{"pid":"a14541f93e48dbfd0b72acdd7108837c1d5c70e2","tid":1238422,"uid":171574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T23:21:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04f04e589dbd78115428120f56a5f2804acce06d","tid":1238422,"uid":5574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T23:28:30.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"54735199be9454a131e7b21eb3956c247abcd02f","tid":1238422,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T23:56:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec5328e06b817ae79489bf3640eedda046963cd3","tid":1238422,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T23:56:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50d58b2b6ab9261ded005b16a79659a6e759c192","tid":1238422,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:33:27.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ee0cbacb2a52e297b63f4bd5a93c982ecd0bfe8b","tid":1238422,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:39:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0838af6ee851a426d344449c52f182c9cd2b7038","tid":1238422,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:21:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60001bad7f7b973e5b88e39a0c1e47bb85b4e9b","tid":1238422,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:33:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27130e3062d5425c0091fec7813eceb34100e063","tid":1238422,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:00:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee3b888427c0feafe369a4c85f7f42a6e4607f8","tid":1238422,"uid":226819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:06:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97ab8fc2bb27a9352a0aef881d70b7ae7c827e81","tid":1238422,"uid":226819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:07:32.000Z","msg":"啱ar 一個唔覺意就拖慢左大家預備工作進度"},{"pid":"ed75f1bb3dab41e2d9580488bf413d23e294f904","tid":1238422,"uid":174530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:10:16.000Z","msg":"呢個post都冇source冇fact check<br />\n唔好推"},{"pid":"fb2c96fa30009bbe4c9c00c98cca92f33cb12357","tid":1238422,"uid":227711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:19:40.000Z","msg":"我冇信，但都入左去推左一下。反省<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb95ea7cdbbe3e7da7ec974cb6eea4c0601efba4","tid":1238422,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed75f1bb3dab41e2d9580488bf413d23e294f904","tid":1238422,"uid":174530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:10:16.000Z","msg":"呢個post都冇source冇fact check<br />\n唔好推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:21:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8423b4a05964231c23fe45339aa3d39843d79269","tid":1238422,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:31:51.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe23334a1f23432c726267388f7740340980eca","tid":1238422,"uid":81698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:23:02.000Z","msg":"問題係義士受重傷點都唔會敢告 盞民憤<br />\n傷得咁重警犬要查點會查唔到？<br />\n<br />\n但家人堅持唔公開 作為專業醫生護士又真係唔會講<br />\n<br />\n講到尾 有人證實到佢無事未？"}]}